1/2 tsp cumin seeds
1 (2-inch cinnamon stick) or 1 tsp
1 cup diced yellow onion
1 green chilli pepper, stemmed, seeded, and minced (serrano for spicy, jalapeno for milder)
4 garlic cloves, minced
1 T finely minced ginger root
